Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.57,0:00:16.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Absorbent and yellow and porous is he
Dialogue: 1,0:00:16.74,0:00:18.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.74,0:00:18.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:00:18.58,0:00:20.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如果四处探险是你的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.58,0:00:20.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If nautical nonsense be something you wish
Dialogue: 1,0:00:20.79,0:00:22.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.79,0:00:22.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:00:22.54,0:00:24.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就敲敲甲板让大鱼开路
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.54,0:00:24.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then drop on the deck and flop like a fish
Dialogue: 1,0:00:24.88,0:00:26.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.88,0:00:26.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:00:26.04,0:00:26.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.04,0:00:26.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ready
Dialogue: 1,0:00:26.67,0:00:36.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.67,0:00:36.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.51,0:00:41.02,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1381.518,382)}海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.39,0:00:45.02,画面,,0,0,0,,{\i1\pos(1480,905)}海绵宝宝呈现
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.69,0:00:47.31,画面,,0,0,0,,{\i1\pos(1442,905)}潮间带
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.06,0:00:50.90,画面,,0,0,0,,{\i1}海星一家缩小记
Dialogue: 1,0:00:51.35,0:00:54.32,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,你正在穿越一个海底次元
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.35,0:00:54.32,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,You are traveling through an aquatic dimension.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.44,0:00:53.28,注释,,0,0,0,,翻译 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.69,0:00:55.53,注释,,0,0,0,,本字幕仅限学习交流 严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 1,0:00:54.32,0:00:57.03,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个次元不仅有着欢笑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.32,0:00:57.03,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,A dimension not only of laughs and giggles
Dialogue: 1,0:00:57.95,0:01:00.50,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有止不住从鼻子笑喷出来的牛奶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.95,0:01:00.50,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,but of uncontrollable nose milk.
Dialogue: 1,0:01:01.45,0:01:03.60,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,等到一切开始疯狂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.45,0:01:03.60,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,When things start to get coocoo
Dialogue: 1,0:01:03.60,0:01:06.39,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就很有可能进入了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.60,0:01:06.39,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,there's a pretty good chance you may have just entered
Dialogue: 1,0:01:06.67,0:01:08.16,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,潮间带
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.67,0:01:08.16,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,"The Tidal Zone!"
Dialogue: 1,0:01:10.90,0:01:13.27,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.90,0:01:13.27,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,And we're back!
Dialogue: 1,0:01:14.38,0:01:16.75,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,《派大星秀》下一组嘉宾
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.38,0:01:16.75,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Our next guest on "The Patrick Show"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.38,0:01:22.81,画面,,0,0,0,,{\i1}派大星秀
Dialogue: 1,0:01:16.75,0:01:22.65,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,是多才多艺的类
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.75,0:01:22.65,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,are the wonderfully talented Captain Quaaa...
Dialogue: 1,0:01:23.17,0:01:25.17,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,类
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.17,0:01:25.17,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Quaaa...
Dialogue: 1,0:01:30.27,0:01:33.72,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,类星体船长与派大机
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.27,0:01:33.72,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Captain Quasar and Pat-Tron!
Dialogue: 1,0:01:44.17,0:01:46.99,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎参加本节目
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.17,0:01:46.99,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welcome to the show, fellas.
Dialogue: 1,0:01:46.99,0:01:48.58,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,飞船不错
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.99,0:01:48.58,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cool spaceship.
Dialogue: 1,0:01:49.67,0:01:51.62,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们是打哪来的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.67,0:01:51.62,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where are you guys from?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:52.97,0:01:54.67,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,外太空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.97,0:01:54.67,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Outer space.
Dialogue: 1,0:01:55.15,0:01:57.30,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,脸太孔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.15,0:01:57.30,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Out her face?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:57.55,0:02:00.50,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  就是外太空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.55,0:02:00.50,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,No. Just outer space.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:00.50,0:02:03.10,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,外总比内强
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.50,0:02:03.10,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, better out than in!
Dialogue: 1,0:02:09.68,0:02:12.85,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大机  都跟你说了要关掉罐头笑声
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.68,0:02:12.85,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pat-Tron, I told you to turn off your laugh track.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:12.85,0:02:15.32,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,罐头笑声会害他齿轮受损
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.85,0:02:15.32,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,It always strips his gears.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:15.86,0:02:17.12,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家不用怕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.86,0:02:17.12,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, folks.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:17.12,0:02:18.65,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来修
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.12,0:02:18.65,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can fix it.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:26.47,0:02:28.25,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,修不好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.47,0:02:28.25,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't fix it!
Dialogue: 1,0:02:28.25,0:02:29.71,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,放我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.25,0:02:29.71,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me out!
Dialogue: 1,0:02:29.71,0:02:32.25,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,排空机器肠道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.71,0:02:32.25,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Evacuating robo-bowels.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:34.25,0:02:36.88,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,我脑瓜里卡了东西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.25,0:02:36.88,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got something stuck to my melon.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:37.21,0:02:38.66,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我的缩小射线
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.21,0:02:38.66,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's my shrink ray.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:38.66,0:02:40.04,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还以为丢了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.66,0:02:40.04,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,I thought I lost that.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:43.49,0:02:46.08,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,射线害我头好辣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.49,0:02:46.08,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's making my head all spicy!
Dialogue: 1,0:02:46.45,0:02:48.56,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,站住  把缩小射线还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.45,0:02:48.56,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop! Give me back my shrink ray!
Dialogue: 1,0:02:50.22,0:02:53.76,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们好  我的爱讲话主持人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.22,0:02:53.76,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hola, my little chatty show hosts.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:54.87,0:02:57.06,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁想点披萨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.87,0:02:57.06,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who wants to order a pizza?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:58.18,0:03:01.89,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要来份加菠萝和百花香的大号披萨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.18,0:03:01.89,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll take a large with pineapple and potpourri.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.18,0:03:01.89,注释,,0,0,0,,[ 百花香：由干燥的天然芳香植物材料混合制成\N有一种特殊的味道 ]
Dialogue: 1,0:03:03.97,0:03:04.91,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,还给你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.97,0:03:04.91,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:11.02,0:03:13.50,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,现场观众不用怕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.02,0:03:13.50,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fear not, studio audience.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:13.50,0:03:15.70,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,我会帮他们解除缩小
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.50,0:03:15.70,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,I will unshrink them
Dialogue: 1,0:03:15.70,0:03:19.80,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,用我飞船里的生长射线
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.70,0:03:19.80,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,with the growth ray I have in my ship.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:26.55,0:03:29.60,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们房子变得好巨大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.55,0:03:29.60,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Our house is gigantic now!
Dialogue: 1,0:03:30.80,0:03:32.25,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是我口香糖
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.80,0:03:32.25,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here's my gum!
Dialogue: 1,0:03:33.73,0:03:36.11,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,好有电影感
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.73,0:03:36.11,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,And so cinematic.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:36.11,0:03:38.30,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,十分电大感
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.11,0:03:38.30,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's cine-gigantic!
Dialogue: 1,0:03:38.30,0:03:40.32,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,这还算话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.30,0:03:40.32,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is that even a word?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:40.69,0:03:43.15,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,邦妮别逗大水儿了  当然不算话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.69,0:03:43.15,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't be retupulous, Bunny, of course not.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:43.15,0:03:45.86,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,变小一定会很有趣大感
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.15,0:03:45.86,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Being small is gonna be fun-gigantic!
Dialogue: 1,0:03:45.86,0:03:47.85,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,最后一个到大臭袜那边的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.86,0:03:47.85,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Last one to the big, stinky sock
Dialogue: 1,0:03:47.85,0:03:49.37,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,变烂鱼卵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.85,0:03:49.37,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,is a rotten fish egg!
Dialogue: 1,0:03:49.37,0:03:50.66,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,好好笑  老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.37,0:03:50.66,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good one, Dad!
Dialogue: 1,0:03:52.22,0:03:53.55,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,要跳吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.22,0:03:53.55,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Shall we?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:54.81,0:03:57.90,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,小小小小小小小
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.81,0:03:57.90,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Small, small, small, small, small, small, small
Dialogue: 1,0:04:00.25,0:04:01.25,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,微小
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.25,0:04:01.25,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Diminutive.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:05.72,0:04:06.76,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,细小
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.72,0:04:06.76,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tiny.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:08.02,0:04:09.22,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,渺小
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.02,0:04:09.22,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Puny.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:11.22,0:04:12.20,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,小不隆冬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.22,0:04:12.20,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Itty-bitty.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:13.10,0:04:14.48,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,小不点儿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.10,0:04:14.48,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Teensy-weensy.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:15.02,0:04:15.95,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,小
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.02,0:04:15.95,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Small.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:17.60,0:04:18.82,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.60,0:04:18.82,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lovely.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:21.25,0:04:22.57,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,别闹了  阿尿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.25,0:04:22.57,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not now, Tinkle!
Dialogue: 1,0:04:27.91,0:04:31.04,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,希望派大爷也能来一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.91,0:04:31.04,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wish GrandPat were here to enjoy this.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:33.40,0:04:33.82,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.40,0:04:33.82,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.08,0:04:37.88,画面,,0,0,0,,{\i1}学校慢行
Dialogue: 1,0:04:44.07,0:04:45.49,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,就不能让老人家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.07,0:04:45.49,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can't an old man
Dialogue: 1,0:04:45.49,0:04:48.80,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,安安静静玩暴力游戏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.49,0:04:48.80,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,play violent video games in peace anymore?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:49.67,0:04:50.68,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,水
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.67,0:04:50.68,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Water?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:57.29,0:04:59.14,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们缩小了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.29,0:04:59.14,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,We got shrunk.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:59.14,0:05:00.50,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大爷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.14,0:05:00.50,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, GrandPat!
Dialogue: 1,0:05:00.50,0:05:03.19,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以帮忙取下小号毛巾吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.50,0:05:03.19,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can you get us some tiny towels?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:03.35,0:05:04.70,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,害虫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.35,0:05:04.70,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Vermin?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:04.87,0:05:07.82,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就用除虫口气逮住你们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.87,0:05:07.82,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll get you with my bug spray breath!
Dialogue: 1,0:05:12.04,0:05:14.75,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大爷  不要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.04,0:05:14.75,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,GrandPat! No!
Dialogue: 1,0:05:17.52,0:05:19.10,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,跑哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.52,0:05:19.10,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where'd they go?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:22.29,0:05:24.76,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们可以安全在这避难  海星一家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.29,0:05:24.76,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'll be safe in here, Stars.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:25.65,0:05:27.45,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,刚才真是好险
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.65,0:05:27.45,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,That was a close shave.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:27.45,0:05:29.27,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢你们救了咱的小命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.45,0:05:29.27,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you for saving us.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:29.27,0:05:29.90,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.27,0:05:29.90,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:29.90,0:05:32.27,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们替派大爷道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.90,0:05:32.27,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,We apologize for GrandPat.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:32.27,0:05:34.05,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,他以为我们是害虫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.27,0:05:34.05,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,He thinks we're vermin.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:34.22,0:05:36.19,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  跟你们一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.22,0:05:36.19,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Like you.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:36.25,0:05:37.27,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.25,0:05:37.27,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,No worries.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:37.27,0:05:38.77,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们只是围坐在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.27,0:05:38.77,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,We were just sitting down
Dialogue: 1,0:05:38.77,0:05:41.11,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备吃烤薄荷糖
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.77,0:05:41.11,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,to eat our roasted peppermint.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:41.11,0:05:44.96,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,量不算多  不过我们愿意跟你们分享
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.11,0:05:44.96,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's not much, but we're willing to share it with you.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:44.96,0:05:46.06,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,分享什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.96,0:05:46.06,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Share what?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:47.16,0:05:49.15,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  注意礼貌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.16,0:05:49.15,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick! Manners!
Dialogue: 1,0:05:49.15,0:05:49.86,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,薄荷味
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.15,0:05:49.86,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Minty.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:50.69,0:05:51.75,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,我去开
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.69,0:05:51.75,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll get it!
Dialogue: 1,0:05:52.13,0:05:54.70,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,希望还有客人要来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.13,0:05:54.70,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,I do hope it's more guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.62,0:06:01.67,画面,,0,0,0,,{\i1}厨房
Dialogue: 1,0:05:58.10,0:05:59.81,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,看到你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.10,0:05:59.81,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,I see you!
Dialogue: 1,0:05:59.81,0:06:00.69,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大爷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.81,0:06:00.69,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,GrandPat?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:00.69,0:06:02.57,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,要想在野外生存
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.69,0:06:02.57,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,To survive in the wild
Dialogue: 1,0:06:02.57,0:06:06.05,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,最好远离家庭矛盾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.57,0:06:06.05,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,we find it best to stay out of family squabbles.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:06.05,0:06:07.57,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,飞镖鱼一家  分散逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.05,0:06:07.57,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dartfishes, scatter!
Dialogue: 1,0:06:12.07,0:06:13.50,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,接招
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.07,0:06:13.50,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take that!
Dialogue: 1,0:06:14.25,0:06:17.25,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大爷把新朋友吓跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.25,0:06:17.25,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,GrandPat scared our new friends away.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:17.69,0:06:20.07,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,他这次太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.69,0:06:20.07,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,This time he's gone too far.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:20.07,0:06:22.90,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,那他亲爱的家人们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.07,0:06:22.90,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then I guess his beloved family
Dialogue: 1,0:06:22.90,0:06:24.95,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定要来好好教训他了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.90,0:06:24.95,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,is gonna have to teach him a lesson.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:24.95,0:06:26.16,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是我们  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.95,0:06:26.16,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's us, right?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:27.40,0:06:28.45,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.40,0:06:28.45,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:29.14,0:06:32.41,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,捉害虫可气死又饿死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.14,0:06:32.41,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,All this pest-huntin' is making me hangry.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:33.35,0:06:34.43,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,来找找
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.35,0:06:34.43,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's see here.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:35.82,0:06:38.35,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,蛋糕模具来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.82,0:06:38.35,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cake molds away!
Dialogue: 1,0:06:44.30,0:06:45.87,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.30,0:06:45.87,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why you--
Dialogue: 1,0:06:50.60,0:06:51.99,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,可恶的小
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.60,0:06:51.99,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why those little--
Dialogue: 1,0:06:57.48,0:06:59.37,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,害虫要复仇是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.48,0:06:59.37,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Revenge of the vermin, eh?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:04.45,0:07:05.32,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.45,0:07:05.32,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 1,0:07:14.82,0:07:17.87,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,害虫比我家人还聪明
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.82,0:07:17.87,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,These insects are smarter than my family.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:19.44,0:07:22.72,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,行了  不当好老头了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.44,0:07:22.72,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it! No more Mr. Nice Geezer!
Dialogue: 1,0:07:22.72,0:07:25.00,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,假牙  去咬它们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.72,0:07:25.00,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dentures, go get 'em!
Dialogue: 1,0:07:32.80,0:07:33.92,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.80,0:07:33.92,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:33.92,0:07:35.97,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是鲁布多
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.92,0:07:35.97,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am Rube-dor.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:35.97,0:07:39.76,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,我用高科技缩小吸收器
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.97,0:07:39.76,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,I shrunk you down with my futuristic shrink suckers
Dialogue: 1,0:07:39.76,0:07:41.56,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,救了你们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.76,0:07:41.56,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,to save you from harm.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:41.77,0:07:43.01,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢  鲁布多
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.77,0:07:43.01,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Rube-dor.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:43.01,0:07:49.15,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,为你们介绍闪光之城舒曼多
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.01,0:07:44.77,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,And to introduce you
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.77,0:07:49.15,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,to the shimmering, shiny city of Shmandor.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:51.65,0:07:54.28,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,舒曼多是个好地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.65,0:07:54.28,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Shmandor is the place to be.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:54.30,0:07:56.65,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,舒曼多食物美味
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.30,0:07:56.65,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Shmandor has fine dining
Dialogue: 1,0:07:58.21,0:07:59.62,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,住房宽敞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.21,0:07:59.62,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,spacious homes
Dialogue: 1,0:07:59.62,0:08:02.15,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,交通系统一流
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.62,0:08:02.15,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,a state-of-the-art transit system
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.79,0:08:05.46,画面,,0,0,0,,{\i1}照相机 袜子 凉鞋
Dialogue: 1,0:08:02.80,0:08:04.50,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,购物中心好物满满
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.80,0:08:04.50,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,shopping centers.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:04.96,0:08:08.38,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,舒曼多位于深海  十分方便
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.96,0:08:08.38,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,And conveniently located under the sea
Dialogue: 1,0:08:09.09,0:08:13.95,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,整座城市完全由手工吹制玻璃打造
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.09,0:08:13.95,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Shmandor is entirely made of hand-blown glass.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:14.50,0:08:17.72,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,太神了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.50,0:08:17.72,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:17.72,0:08:19.90,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊  可以在这定居吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.72,0:08:19.90,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy, can we live here?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:19.90,0:08:21.67,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,当然可以了  孩子们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.90,0:08:21.67,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure, we can, kids.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:21.67,0:08:26.04,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,舒曼多好美  让我好想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.67,0:08:26.04,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Shmandor is so beautiful, it makes me feel like...
Dialogue: 1,0:08:26.04,0:08:28.22,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.04,0:08:28.22,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Singing
Dialogue: 1,0:08:28.22,0:08:29.21,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,慢着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.22,0:08:29.21,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 1,0:08:29.45,0:08:32.42,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,舒曼多不可以唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.45,0:08:32.42,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's no singing allowed in Shmandor!
Dialogue: 1,0:08:33.75,0:08:35.94,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就是原因
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.75,0:08:35.94,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,And that's why!
Dialogue: 1,0:08:36.21,0:08:36.97,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.21,0:08:36.97,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yuck.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:36.97,0:08:39.65,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能唱歌的地方怎么住得了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.97,0:08:39.65,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who wants to live in a place where you can't sing?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:40.41,0:08:44.12,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是好险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.41,0:08:44.12,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,That was a close one
Dialogue: 1,0:08:44.12,0:08:47.38,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,更险的来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.12,0:08:47.38,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,And here comes a closer one
Dialogue: 1,0:08:51.44,0:08:54.12,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们太小  碾不到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.44,0:08:54.12,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're too small to be run over.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:55.81,0:09:00.01,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,如果我是脏跳蚤  会躲在哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.81,0:09:00.01,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, where would I hide if I was a filthy flea?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:00.01,0:09:03.57,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,该来继续狠狠教训派大爷了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.01,0:09:03.57,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think it's time to resume GrandPat's lesson.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:05.80,0:09:08.98,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在派大机里面学来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.80,0:09:08.98,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,I picked this one up inside Pat-tron.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:13.73,0:09:17.23,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,滑板车闹鬼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.73,0:09:17.23,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,My scooter is haunted!
Dialogue: 1,0:09:35.42,0:09:39.90,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,别整我轮子  不然就烤了你们这群鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.42,0:09:39.90,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Quit spookin' my wheels or I'll roast you ghosts!
Dialogue: 1,0:09:43.77,0:09:46.72,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,埃及  我爱埃及
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.77,0:09:46.72,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Egypt? I love Egypt!
Dialogue: 1,0:09:50.82,0:09:53.05,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我恨木乃伊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.82,0:09:53.05,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I hate mummies!
Dialogue: 1,0:09:53.42,0:09:55.40,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定要回家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.42,0:09:55.40,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,I gotta get home!
Dialogue: 1,0:09:55.83,0:09:56.60,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,真好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.83,0:09:56.60,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,That was fun
Dialogue: 1,0:09:56.60,0:10:00.45,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我们这么小  观众看不到怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.60,0:10:00.45,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,but what if we're too small for the audience to see us?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:00.45,0:10:02.36,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家来看看我找到什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.45,0:10:02.36,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, guys, look what I found.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.28,0:10:05.75,画面,,0,0,0,,{\i1}海草与珊瑚巨大生长肥料
Dialogue: 1,0:10:02.68,0:10:04.38,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,巨大生长肥料
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.68,0:10:04.38,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Jumbo Grow plant food!
Dialogue: 1,0:10:04.38,0:10:05.33,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  小心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.38,0:10:05.33,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, be careful!
Dialogue: 1,0:10:05.33,0:10:07.16,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,要长大了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.33,0:10:07.16,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's time to grow up!
Dialogue: 1,0:10:11.66,0:10:14.71,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在小字看得到了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.66,0:10:14.71,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now I can see the fine print, Patrick.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.71,0:10:18.72,画面,,0,0,0,,{\i1}警告 本品可使生长缓慢植物长大\N若使用于其他物品将会缩小
Dialogue: 1,0:10:14.95,0:10:18.72,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,肥料会让植物长大  但会让人缩小
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.95,0:10:18.72,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,It grows plants, but it shrinks people.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:18.72,0:10:23.81,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,你把大家缩成亚原子级别的大小了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.72,0:10:20.01,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,You shrunk us down
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.01,0:10:23.81,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,to the sub-atomic teensy-weensy level.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:24.86,0:10:27.85,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,今晚的节目演不完了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.86,0:10:27.85,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now I'll never finish tonight's show.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:27.85,0:10:29.62,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,团结起来  海星一家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.85,0:10:29.62,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stay together, Stars.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:29.62,0:10:31.65,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,这里应该有出口
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.62,0:10:31.65,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think there's a way out of here!
Dialogue: 1,0:10:33.80,0:10:36.05,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,看  回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.80,0:10:36.05,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look, we're home.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:36.05,0:10:38.40,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,一切都恢复正常了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.05,0:10:38.40,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everything's back to normal.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:38.40,0:10:39.50,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.40,0:10:39.50,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:39.50,0:10:40.40,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.50,0:10:40.40,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 1,0:10:41.31,0:10:43.92,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,只不过月球变大眼球了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.31,0:10:43.92,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Except the Moon is a big eyeball now.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:47.77,0:10:49.96,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,微生物太迷人了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.77,0:10:49.96,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Micro-critters are fascinatin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.87,0:10:57.51,画面,,0,0,0,,{\i1}大泡弹
Dialogue: 1,0:10:50.12,0:10:52.05,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,它们是怎么做到这么精密复杂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.12,0:10:52.05,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,How can be they be so sophisticated
Dialogue: 1,0:10:52.05,0:10:54.15,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,还能这么小的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.05,0:10:54.15,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,when they're so dang little?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:55.02,0:10:56.70,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,很高兴没人在看着我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.02,0:10:56.70,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Glad no one's watchin' me.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:08.37,0:11:10.75,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,旁白奶奶常常教导我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.37,0:11:10.75,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Grandma Frenchy always said
Dialogue: 1,0:11:10.75,0:11:12.92,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,别为小事斤斤计较
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.75,0:11:12.92,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Don't sweat the small stuff."
Dialogue: 1,0:11:12.92,0:11:14.77,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,在这个小小的世界里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.92,0:11:14.77,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,And in this small world
Dialogue: 1,0:11:14.77,0:11:17.77,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,浓缩的小东西都是精华
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.77,0:11:17.77,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,where good things come in small packages
Dialogue: 1,0:11:17.77,0:11:22.10,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,不难理解  小小的细节决定成败
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.77,0:11:19.57,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,it's no small wonder
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.57,0:11:22.10,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,that it's the little things that mean a lot.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:22.10,0:11:25.65,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,尽在这小小的凌晨时光里的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.10,0:11:25.65,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Especially in the wee small hours of
Dialogue: 1,0:11:25.65,0:11:27.47,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,潮间带
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.65,0:11:27.47,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,"The Tidal Zone."
