Dialogue: 1,0:11:44.17,0:11:45.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请你想象
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.17,0:11:45.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Imagine if you will
Dialogue: 1,0:11:45.97,0:11:48.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小镇裤头村
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.97,0:11:48.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the town of Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:11:48.39,0:11:53.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在来想象这里的居民都是机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.39,0:11:53.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now imagine if everyone who lived there was a robot
Dialogue: 1,0:11:53.71,0:11:55.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为你呈现
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.71,0:11:55.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Submitted for your approval
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.23,0:11:57.36,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1192,818)}裤头村
Dialogue: 1,0:11:57.24,0:11:59.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,二进制村之旅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.24,0:11:59.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a trip to Binary Bottom
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.90,0:12:00.03,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1192,818)}二进制村
Dialogue: 1,0:12:17.50,0:12:19.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准准  准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.50,0:12:19.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm re-re-ready
Dialogue: 1,0:12:19.06,0:12:20.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准准  准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.06,0:12:20.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm re-re-ready
Dialogue: 1,0:12:20.42,0:12:22.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准准  准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.42,0:12:22.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm re-re-ready
Dialogue: 1,0:12:22.05,0:12:23.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准准  备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.05,0:12:23.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm red-red-ready
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.93,0:12:27.55,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1472,742)}油
Dialogue: 1,0:12:31.50,0:12:33.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早安  海绵机
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.50,0:12:33.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Morning, SpongeBot
Dialogue: 1,0:12:33.69,0:12:35.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你今天样子真帅气
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.69,0:12:35.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're looking handsome today
Dialogue: 1,0:12:50.87,0:12:51.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.87,0:12:51.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good--
Dialogue: 1,0:12:51.98,0:12:53.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早安  机器蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.98,0:12:53.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,good morning, Robo-Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:13:01.77,0:13:03.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你想玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.77,0:13:03.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You wanna play
Dialogue: 1,0:13:03.45,0:13:05.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我知道你想玩什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.45,0:13:05.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know what you want
Dialogue: 1,0:13:08.95,0:13:12.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗  对激光温柔一点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.95,0:13:12.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary, be gentle with the little laser
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.73,0:13:19.48,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1544,654)}工作
Dialogue: 1,0:13:22.27,0:13:23.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该去上班了  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.27,0:13:23.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Time for work, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:13:23.47,0:13:25.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等我回家了我再来跟你玩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.47,0:13:25.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll play with you more when I get home
Dialogue: 1,0:13:32.41,0:13:34.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.41,0:13:34.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no, Gare-bearings
Dialogue: 1,0:13:34.45,0:13:36.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,必须待在家里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.45,0:13:36.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You have to stay here at home
Dialogue: 1,0:13:44.12,0:13:45.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,往左边一点点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.12,0:13:45.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A little more to the left
Dialogue: 1,0:13:51.01,0:13:52.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.01,0:13:52.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Almost there
Dialogue: 1,0:13:52.42,0:13:54.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完完完美
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.42,0:13:54.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,P-p-p-perfect
Dialogue: 1,0:13:54.30,0:13:56.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见  小小小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.30,0:13:56.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See you later, G-G-G-Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:14:01.23,0:14:01.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,终于
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.23,0:14:01.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Finally
Dialogue: 1,0:14:01.96,0:14:05.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有个能让我快快乐乐陪在身边的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.96,0:14:05.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,someone whose company I actually enjoy--
Dialogue: 1,0:14:05.45,0:14:06.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.45,0:14:06.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,me
Dialogue: 1,0:14:12.18,0:14:13.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该上班了  章鱼机
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.18,0:14:13.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Time for work, Squidbot
Dialogue: 1,0:14:14.20,0:14:15.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该上班了  章鱼机
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.20,0:14:15.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Time for work, Squidbot
Dialogue: 1,0:14:15.82,0:14:17.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该上班了  章鱼机
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.82,0:14:17.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Time for work, Squidbot
Dialogue: 1,0:14:17.47,0:14:18.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该上班了  章鱼机
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.47,0:14:18.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Time for work, Squidbot
Dialogue: 1,0:14:19.22,0:14:22.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我断电滚远点  海绵机
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.22,0:14:22.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Power down and leave me alone, SpongeBot
Dialogue: 1,0:14:22.00,0:14:23.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只剩十五分钟了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.00,0:14:23.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've still got 15 minutes
Dialogue: 1,0:14:24.84,0:14:26.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  章鱼机
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.84,0:14:26.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Squidbot
Dialogue: 1,0:14:26.17,0:14:27.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  章鱼机
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.17,0:14:27.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Squidbot
Dialogue: 1,0:14:27.51,0:14:28.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  章鱼机
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.51,0:14:28.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Squidbot
Dialogue: 1,0:14:28.95,0:14:30.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,走开
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.95,0:14:30.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go away
Dialogue: 1,0:14:32.83,0:14:35.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得住那家伙隔壁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.83,0:14:35.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am going to have to live next to that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.39,0:14:37.93,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(998,222)}自爆
Dialogue: 1,0:14:43.07,0:14:44.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,敲敲门
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.07,0:14:44.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Knock, knock, knock
Dialogue: 1,0:14:44.62,0:14:47.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大机  我要去上班了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.62,0:14:47.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey Pat-Tron, I'm going to work
Dialogue: 1,0:14:47.28,0:14:49.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我跟你一起走  海绵机
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.28,0:14:49.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going with you, SpongeBot
Dialogue: 1,0:14:49.70,0:14:51.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得补充燃料
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.70,0:14:51.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I gotta fuel up
Dialogue: 1,0:14:51.10,0:14:54.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.10,0:14:54.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hooray
Dialogue: 1,0:14:59.13,0:15:01.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大机正处于充电模式
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.13,0:15:01.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pat-Tron is currently in recharge mode
Dialogue: 1,0:15:02.61,0:15:03.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.61,0:15:03.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,OK, buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:15:03.75,0:15:06.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我回家会给你带燃料回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.75,0:15:06.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll bring you some fuel on my way back home
Dialogue: 1,0:15:09.26,0:15:11.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是非得迟到的话  就把钥匙给我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.26,0:15:11.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If you're going to be late, give me the key
Dialogue: 1,0:15:12.46,0:15:13.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  章鱼机
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.46,0:15:13.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Squidbot
Dialogue: 1,0:15:13.60,0:15:14.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.60,0:15:14.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But
Dialogue: 1,0:15:14.30,0:15:17.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我钥匙骨头连着手指骨头  给不了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.30,0:15:17.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The key bone's connected to the finger bone
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.02,0:15:25.69,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(538,572)}电池王
Dialogue: 1,0:15:26.36,0:15:30.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你被开除了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.36,0:15:30.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're fired
Dialogue: 1,0:15:33.67,0:15:34.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.67,0:15:34.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Bot-O
Dialogue: 1,0:15:34.82,0:15:36.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我刚卡在开除模式了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.82,0:15:36.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got stuck in the firing mode
Dialogue: 1,0:15:37.67,0:15:39.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要被开除了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.67,0:15:39.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,To be fired
Dialogue: 1,0:15:40.57,0:15:43.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没人会被开除  你个机器懒鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.57,0:15:43.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nobody's getting fired, you robo-loafer
Dialogue: 1,0:15:43.67,0:15:45.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所有人去工作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.67,0:15:45.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everybody get to work
Dialogue: 1,0:15:50.55,0:15:53.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,电池堡煎得滋滋作响
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.55,0:15:53.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Krabby Batteries are sizzlin'
Dialogue: 1,0:15:53.17,0:15:54.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来加调料了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.17,0:15:54.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now it's time for condiments
Dialogue: 1,0:16:03.20,0:16:04.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快上菜  海绵机
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.20,0:16:04.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Food up, SpongeBot
Dialogue: 1,0:16:04.65,0:16:07.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快来两份电池堡  加洋葱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.65,0:16:07.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gimme two batteries on a barge and make 'em cry
Dialogue: 1,0:16:12.92,0:16:14.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,机器蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.92,0:16:14.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Robo-Gary?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:14.40,0:16:15.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼机
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.40,0:16:15.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidbot?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:15.82,0:16:17.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.82,0:16:17.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:16:21.08,0:16:22.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蜗鱼章
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.08,0:16:22.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary-Squid?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:22.17,0:16:23.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.17,0:16:23.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squid-Gary?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:24.03,0:16:26.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,无法计算
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.03,0:16:26.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Does not compute
Dialogue: 1,0:16:27.15,0:16:31.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把你家脏兮兮的机器蜗牛弄下去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.15,0:16:31.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get your filthy robo-snail off my head
Dialogue: 1,0:16:34.64,0:16:35.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.64,0:16:35.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary
