Dialogue: 1,0:16:55.62,0:16:59.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,迟早要给这条随地大便的寄生虫断电
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.62,0:16:59.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've gotta cut off this pooping parasite
Dialogue: 1,0:16:59.29,0:17:02.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  这到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.29,0:17:02.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, what the kelp is going on in here?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:06.96,0:17:10.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我回来  你们这群镀镍的傻蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.96,0:17:10.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come back here, you nickel-plated nincompoops
Dialogue: 1,0:17:15.25,0:17:18.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老机  你又忘了上发条了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.25,0:17:18.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plankbot, you forgot to wind yourself again
Dialogue: 1,0:17:18.72,0:17:19.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢你  凯伦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.72,0:17:19.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Karen
Dialogue: 1,0:17:19.72,0:17:21.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的血肉之躯老婆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.72,0:17:21.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,my flesh and blood wife
Dialogue: 1,0:17:21.70,0:17:23.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你放心  我会抓到他的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.70,0:17:23.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, I'll get him
Dialogue: 1,0:17:24.83,0:17:25.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  凯伦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.83,0:17:25.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Karen
Dialogue: 1,0:17:25.55,0:17:27.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗有经过这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.55,0:17:27.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did Gary come through here?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:27.07,0:17:29.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他往那边走了  爱笑鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.07,0:17:29.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He went thataway, Chuckles
Dialogue: 1,0:17:29.53,0:17:30.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢谢  谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.53,0:17:30.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Th-th-th-thank you
Dialogue: 1,0:17:31.74,0:17:34.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我妈交代过我千万别嫁机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.74,0:17:34.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mama told me not to marry a robot
Dialogue: 1,0:17:35.78,0:17:37.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快让开
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.78,0:17:37.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gangway
Dialogue: 1,0:17:37.05,0:17:38.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,机器人出逃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.05,0:17:38.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Runaway robot
