Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.32,0:17:42.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, pardon me
Dialogue: 1,0:17:42.75,0:17:43.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思  借过一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.75,0:17:43.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, pardon me
Dialogue: 1,0:17:43.97,0:17:45.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思  借过一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.97,0:17:45.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, pardon me
Dialogue: 1,0:17:52.40,0:17:58.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是谁侵扰了珊卓的神圣电子屋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.40,0:17:58.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who disturbs the sacred dome of Sandroid?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:58.97,0:18:02.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要捆住你们的传动装置
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.97,0:18:02.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll hogtie your actuators
Dialogue: 1,0:18:02.85,0:18:04.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊卓  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.85,0:18:04.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandroid, wait
Dialogue: 1,0:18:04.17,0:18:07.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗还年轻  传动装置千万不能捆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.17,0:18:07.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary is too young to have his actuators hogtied
Dialogue: 1,0:18:07.40,0:18:09.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要黑进你们的硬件
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.40,0:18:09.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll hack your hard drives
Dialogue: 1,0:18:09.51,0:18:11.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们这群自动化白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.51,0:18:11.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you cybernetic simpletons
Dialogue: 1,0:18:15.95,0:18:18.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.95,0:18:18.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, there you go
