Dialogue: 1,0:18:33.67,0:18:35.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,机器狗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.67,0:18:35.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Robo-dog
Dialogue: 1,0:18:35.12,0:18:37.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来买机器狗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.12,0:18:37.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get your robo-dog
Dialogue: 1,0:18:47.39,0:18:48.92,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,润乐湖
