Dialogue: 1,0:18:48.92,0:18:51.05,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,酷乐湖怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.92,0:18:51.05,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,What happened to Goo Lagoon?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:51.05,0:18:53.95,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在哪个时空来着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.05,0:18:53.95,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where in space and time am I?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:54.32,0:18:57.22,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来我在前一次大灾变那边转错弯了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.32,0:18:57.22,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looks like I took a wrong turn at the last apocalypse.
Dialogue: 1,0:18:57.22,0:18:58.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.22,0:18:58.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Danger
Dialogue: 1,0:18:58.53,0:18:59.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,机器暴民
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.53,0:18:59.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Rogue Robot
Dialogue: 1,0:18:59.97,0:19:00.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.97,0:19:00.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary, wait
Dialogue: 1,0:19:01.05,0:19:02.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,回来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.05,0:19:02.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come back
Dialogue: 1,0:19:03.07,0:19:07.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁这么大胆  敢侵犯珊卓
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.07,0:19:07.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who dares defy Sandroid?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:07.25,0:19:09.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要毁灭你们所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.25,0:19:09.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna destroy all of you
Dialogue: 1,0:19:11.12,0:19:14.85,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,这群破铜烂铁想要我赘肉当燃料
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.12,0:19:14.85,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,These junk heaps want my flab for fuel!
Dialogue: 1,0:19:19.12,0:19:20.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.12,0:19:20.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, Gary
