Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.80,0:19:23.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do I do now?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:23.55,0:19:24.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想想办法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.55,0:19:24.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Got to think
