Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.55,0:19:58.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's not gonna stop
Dialogue: 1,0:20:12.42,0:20:14.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟机器蝶好好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.42,0:20:14.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Play nice with the flutterbot
Dialogue: 1,0:20:52.22,0:20:54.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太神了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.22,0:20:54.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Amazing
Dialogue: 1,0:20:56.69,0:21:03.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,禁止在珊卓面前开闪光灯拍照
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.69,0:20:59.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Flash photography is forbidden
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.28,0:21:03.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in the presence of Sandroid
Dialogue: 1,0:21:03.17,0:21:07.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们全部都要让我同化
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.17,0:21:07.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You will all be assimilated
Dialogue: 1,0:21:07.22,0:21:10.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样就可以亲亲密密在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.22,0:21:10.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So we can all be as close as peas in a pod
Dialogue: 1,0:21:12.29,0:21:13.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太神
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.29,0:21:13.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ama--
Dialogue: 1,0:21:19.20,0:21:24.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你害我又被大铁怪困住了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.20,0:21:20.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, this is another
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.93,0:21:24.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,fine metallic monstrosity you've got me into
Dialogue: 1,0:21:24.52,0:21:26.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,往好的方面看  章鱼机
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.52,0:21:26.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at it this way, Squidbot
Dialogue: 1,0:21:26.27,0:21:29.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在就有机会跟所有邻居叙叙旧了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.27,0:21:27.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now we'll have a chance
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.18,0:21:29.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to catch up with all our neighbors
