Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.13,0:21:52.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Rise of the robots
Dialogue: 1,0:21:54.60,0:21:56.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我附议
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.60,0:21:56.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I second that
Dialogue: 1,0:21:59.27,0:22:01.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说机器人无法取代我们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.27,0:22:01.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Robots can never replace us, you say?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:02.33,0:22:05.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然而动画片里一切皆有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.33,0:22:05.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, anything can happen in a cartoon
Dialogue: 1,0:22:05.49,0:22:07.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而这部动画片则来自
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.49,0:22:07.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,especially if that cartoon is from
