Dialogue: 1,0:22:21.55,0:22:23.76,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,闪电莓  闪电莓
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.55,0:22:23.76,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lightning berries, lightning berries
Dialogue: 1,0:22:23.76,0:22:25.95,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在扫描闪电莓
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.76,0:22:25.95,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm scanning for lightning berries
