Dialogue: 1,0:22:25.95,0:22:28.49,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,摘给亲爱痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.95,0:22:28.49,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,For dear, old, Mr. Plankton
