Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.13,0:22:53.35,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Camper Patrick!
Dialogue: 1,0:22:54.38,0:22:57.67,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,你居然把闪电莓都吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.38,0:22:57.67,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you ate all the lightning berries.
