Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.87,0:23:01.31,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is that my hat?
Dialogue: 1,0:23:01.31,0:23:02.74,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,不  先等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.31,0:23:02.74,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,No. Wait, just a sec--
Dialogue: 1,0:23:05.60,0:23:06.92,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,闪电莓
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.60,0:23:06.92,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lightning berries
Dialogue: 1,0:23:06.92,0:23:09.42,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,与凯伦的计算机电路
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.92,0:23:09.42,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,and Karen's computer circuitry.
Dialogue: 1,0:23:09.42,0:23:10.85,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,这奇妙的组合
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.42,0:23:10.85,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,A potent combination
Dialogue: 1,0:23:10.85,0:23:13.67,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,将导致一场震惊无比的意识交换
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.85,0:23:13.67,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,which results in a shocking mind switch.
Dialogue: 1,0:23:14.15,0:23:15.95,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,这种常事  尽在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.15,0:23:15.95,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,A common occurrence here in...
Dialogue: 1,0:23:17.82,0:23:19.10,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,潮间带
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.82,0:23:19.10,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,"The Tidal Zone."
Dialogue: 1,0:23:28.39,0:23:29.87,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后珊迪说“好”
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.39,0:23:29.87,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,And then Sandy said "yeah"
Dialogue: 1,0:23:29.87,0:23:31.20,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,哈维说“好”
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.87,0:23:31.20,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,and Harvey goes "yeah."
Dialogue: 1,0:23:31.20,0:23:32.80,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后凯文说“好”
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.20,0:23:32.80,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,And then Kevin said "yeah."
Dialogue: 1,0:23:34.26,0:23:35.97,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家都在说好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.26,0:23:35.97,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everybody was saying yeah.
Dialogue: 1,0:23:35.97,0:23:36.97,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.97,0:23:36.97,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Enough!
Dialogue: 1,0:23:36.97,0:23:38.77,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,你干嘛找我说话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.97,0:23:38.77,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why are you talking to me?
Dialogue: 1,0:23:38.77,0:23:41.19,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在留下美好回忆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.77,0:23:41.19,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm making memories.
Dialogue: 1,0:23:41.37,0:23:42.97,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我记好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.37,0:23:42.97,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, remember this.
Dialogue: 1,0:23:44.95,0:23:47.22,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,凯伦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.95,0:23:47.22,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Karen!
Dialogue: 1,0:23:47.99,0:23:49.24,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,总算来了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.99,0:23:49.24,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,There she is!
Dialogue: 1,0:23:50.07,0:23:51.70,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,你都去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.07,0:23:51.70,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where the heck have you been?
Dialogue: 1,0:23:51.70,0:23:54.37,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要的闪电莓在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.70,0:23:54.37,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,And where are those lightning berries I asked you for?
Dialogue: 1,0:23:54.37,0:23:55.62,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,我吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.37,0:23:55.62,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,I ate them.
Dialogue: 1,0:23:55.62,0:23:57.25,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在说什么胡话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.62,0:23:57.25,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 1,0:23:57.25,0:23:59.20,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,你吃不了东西
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.25,0:23:59.20,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know you don't eat.
Dialogue: 1,0:24:00.17,0:24:02.02,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,快带我回家去
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.17,0:24:02.02,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now take me home.
Dialogue: 1,0:24:04.67,0:24:05.45,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.67,0:24:05.45,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, buddy.
Dialogue: 1,0:24:06.15,0:24:07.65,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,快点  要迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.15,0:24:07.65,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on. We're late.
Dialogue: 1,0:24:10.15,0:24:10.73,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.15,0:24:10.73,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Golly.
Dialogue: 1,0:24:12.21,0:24:14.22,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,滑得不错
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.21,0:24:14.22,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sweet ride.
Dialogue: 1,0:24:14.53,0:24:16.20,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,你还挺会过日子
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.53,0:24:16.20,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,You really know how to live.
Dialogue: 1,0:24:23.53,0:24:24.60,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.53,0:24:24.60,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Howdy, boys.
Dialogue: 1,0:24:24.60,0:24:25.80,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,来得正好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.60,0:24:25.80,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're just in time.
Dialogue: 1,0:24:25.80,0:24:28.22,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就快把游戏摆好了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.80,0:24:28.22,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm almost done setting up the game.
Dialogue: 1,0:24:33.11,0:24:34.42,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.11,0:24:34.42,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 1,0:24:35.33,0:24:36.33,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的意识
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.33,0:24:36.33,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,My mind
Dialogue: 1,0:24:36.33,0:24:38.55,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定跟派大星的意识发生了交换
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.33,0:24:38.55,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,must've switched with Patrick's mind
Dialogue: 1,0:24:38.55,0:24:40.54,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,都是闪电莓导致的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.55,0:24:40.54,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,from the lightning berries.
Dialogue: 1,0:24:40.97,0:24:43.32,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,有血有肉有大肚
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.97,0:24:43.32,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Flesh and blood and guts.
Dialogue: 1,0:24:44.02,0:24:46.43,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,我变模拟量了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.02,0:24:46.43,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've gone analog.
Dialogue: 1,0:24:50.50,0:24:52.60,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,原来这俩条是腿
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.50,0:24:52.60,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,So these are legs?
Dialogue: 1,0:24:55.38,0:24:58.87,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,控制活生生的身体不算太难
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.38,0:24:58.87,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,A living body isn't so hard to control.
Dialogue: 1,0:24:59.77,0:25:01.50,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,掌握诀窍了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.77,0:25:01.50,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think I got this.
Dialogue: 1,0:25:05.46,0:25:06.77,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,全都准备好开局了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.46,0:25:06.77,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,All ready to play.
Dialogue: 1,0:25:07.56,0:25:10.90,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,这可是我发明过最难的桌游了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.56,0:25:10.90,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,This here's the toughest board game I ever invented.
Dialogue: 1,0:25:10.90,0:25:13.53,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,要想获胜  就要了解数学
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.90,0:25:13.53,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,In order to win, you need to know math
Dialogue: 1,0:25:13.53,0:25:16.61,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,科学  文学  还有历史
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.53,0:25:16.61,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,science, literature, and history.
Dialogue: 1,0:25:20.58,0:25:25.17,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,2553025的平方根等于多少
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.58,0:25:25.17,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's the square root of 25,553,025?
Dialogue: 1,0:25:26.40,0:25:28.67,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,5055
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.40,0:25:28.67,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,5,055.
Dialogue: 1,0:25:29.25,0:25:30.17,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.25,0:25:30.17,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:25:32.27,0:25:33.97,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,液体流速增大
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.27,0:25:33.97,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,The increase in speed of a liquid...
Dialogue: 1,0:25:33.97,0:25:36.26,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,伯努利原理
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.97,0:25:36.26,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,The law of fluid dynamics.
Dialogue: 1,0:25:36.84,0:25:38.55,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,后结构主义
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.84,0:25:38.55,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Post-structuralism.
Dialogue: 1,0:25:38.55,0:25:40.70,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,公元395年
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.55,0:25:40.70,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,395 AD.
Dialogue: 1,0:25:40.70,0:25:42.56,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,亚特兰蒂斯的沉没
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.70,0:25:42.56,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,The sinking of Atlantis.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.56,0:25:43.60,画面,,0,0,0,,{\i1}获胜
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.60,0:25:45.39,画面,,0,0,0,,{\i1\pos(1086,905)}智多星
Dialogue: 1,0:25:44.02,0:25:45.10,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,我赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.02,0:25:45.10,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,I win!
Dialogue: 1,0:25:49.75,0:25:50.95,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,好棒  凯伦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.75,0:25:50.95,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's great, Karen.
Dialogue: 1,0:25:50.95,0:25:52.20,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,实在太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.95,0:25:52.20,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Real great.
Dialogue: 1,0:25:52.20,0:25:55.33,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在我就只能拿辐射苹果
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.20,0:25:55.33,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, I'll have to substitute radioactive apples...
Dialogue: 1,0:25:55.72,0:25:57.30,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,代替闪电莓了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.72,0:25:57.30,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,For the lightning berries.
Dialogue: 1,0:26:01.00,0:26:02.32,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.00,0:26:02.32,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is that me?
Dialogue: 1,0:26:02.67,0:26:05.16,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,我现在变轮滑鞋了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.67,0:26:05.16,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm a rollie shoe now?
Dialogue: 1,0:26:05.57,0:26:06.61,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,好酷
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.57,0:26:06.61,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cool!
Dialogue: 1,0:26:13.43,0:26:14.17,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,斜坡
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.43,0:26:14.17,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ramp.
Dialogue: 1,0:26:16.40,0:26:18.13,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的海神王啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.40,0:26:18.13,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, my Neptune!
Dialogue: 1,0:26:19.72,0:26:20.92,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.72,0:26:20.92,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Watch it!
Dialogue: 1,0:26:23.92,0:26:27.35,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,别闹了  帮我把这个切开
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.92,0:26:27.35,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop fooling around and help me cut this open.
Dialogue: 1,0:26:28.07,0:26:29.52,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,手术刀给我
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.07,0:26:29.52,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hand me a scalpel.
Dialogue: 1,0:26:32.52,0:26:34.55,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,让我
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.52,0:26:34.55,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me...
Dialogue: 1,0:26:35.47,0:26:36.49,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,拿到了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.47,0:26:36.49,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got it!
Dialogue: 1,0:26:36.62,0:26:38.20,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在快拿给我
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.62,0:26:38.20,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, hand it to me.
Dialogue: 1,0:26:46.49,0:26:47.60,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.49,0:26:47.60,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Careful!
Dialogue: 1,0:26:47.60,0:26:48.93,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,里面都是硫
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.60,0:26:48.93,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's full of sulfuric...
Dialogue: 1,0:26:49.97,0:26:50.87,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,酸
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.97,0:26:50.87,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,acid.
Dialogue: 1,0:26:54.09,0:26:57.02,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  赶紧给你重启吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.09,0:26:57.02,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, time for a robot reboot.
Dialogue: 1,0:27:00.20,0:27:01.48,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我回来
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.20,0:27:01.48,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get back here!
Dialogue: 1,0:27:13.05,0:27:15.25,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,你中了什么邪  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.05,0:27:15.25,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's gotten into you, Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:27:15.25,0:27:17.24,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,你今天不太像你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.25,0:27:17.24,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,You don't seem like yourself today.
Dialogue: 1,0:27:17.24,0:27:19.07,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不是我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.24,0:27:19.07,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm not myself.
Dialogue: 1,0:27:19.54,0:27:22.55,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是凯伦  痞老板的电脑助理
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.54,0:27:22.55,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm Karen, Plankton's computer assistant
Dialogue: 1,0:27:22.55,0:27:24.18,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在在派大星身体里
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.55,0:27:24.18,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,in Patrick's body.
Dialogue: 1,0:27:25.17,0:27:26.59,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们的意识发生了交换
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.17,0:27:26.59,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Our minds got switched
Dialogue: 1,0:27:26.59,0:27:30.27,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,那时我们俩都被闪电莓电到了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.59,0:27:30.27,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,when we were both electrified by lightning berries.
Dialogue: 1,0:27:30.93,0:27:34.22,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,好家伙  意识交换
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.93,0:27:34.22,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hot diggity dog! A mind switch!
Dialogue: 1,0:27:34.95,0:27:37.65,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,来分析一下  交换感觉如何
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.95,0:27:37.65,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's analyze. What's it like?
Dialogue: 1,0:27:38.02,0:27:40.16,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,待在派大星的身体里
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.02,0:27:40.16,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, being in Patrick's body
Dialogue: 1,0:27:40.16,0:27:44.90,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,让我体验到前所未有的感觉  像味觉
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.16,0:27:44.90,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,has opened up senses that I never had like taste.
Dialogue: 1,0:27:46.81,0:27:48.85,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,来  尝个甜甜圈
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.81,0:27:48.85,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here, try a doughnut.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.15,0:27:55.77,画面,,0,0,0,,{\i1}味觉加载中
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.77,0:27:56.52,画面,,0,0,0,,{\i1}加载完毕
Dialogue: 1,0:27:59.58,0:28:02.10,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.58,0:28:02.10,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's delicious!
Dialogue: 1,0:28:02.98,0:28:05.03,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个有什么味道
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.98,0:28:05.03,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's this taste like?
Dialogue: 1,0:28:07.77,0:28:10.26,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个也很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.77,0:28:10.26,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,That tastes pretty good too.
Dialogue: 1,0:28:13.29,0:28:16.46,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,外面还有可以吃的东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.29,0:28:16.46,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are there more things to ingest out here?
Dialogue: 1,0:28:29.64,0:28:32.17,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,我这是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.64,0:28:32.17,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's happening to me?
Dialogue: 1,0:28:32.17,0:28:33.85,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,这叫疼痛
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.17,0:28:33.85,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's called pain.
Dialogue: 1,0:28:35.75,0:28:39.61,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,疼痛  好迷人
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.75,0:28:39.61,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pain. Fascinating.
Dialogue: 1,0:28:41.82,0:28:43.05,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,快来
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.82,0:28:43.05,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 1,0:28:43.05,0:28:46.10,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,踢踢我  让我多疼点
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.05,0:28:46.10,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Kick me for more pain.
Dialogue: 1,0:28:55.04,0:28:56.57,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,快回来
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.04,0:28:56.57,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get back here!
Dialogue: 1,0:28:57.38,0:29:00.27,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,快给轮滑鞋让条道
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.38,0:29:00.27,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Make way for the rollie shoe!
Dialogue: 1,0:29:02.72,0:29:06.38,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,没什么好看的  继续做小屁孩去
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.72,0:29:06.38,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nothing to see here! Go back to your childhoods!
Dialogue: 1,0:29:08.57,0:29:10.47,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在里面没事吧  凯伦
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.57,0:29:10.47,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,You okay in there, Karen?
Dialogue: 1,0:29:12.31,0:29:15.90,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗅觉  不是很行
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.31,0:29:15.90,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sense of smell, not so great.
Dialogue: 1,0:29:16.65,0:29:18.68,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,确实有趣过一阵子
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.65,0:29:18.68,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, it's been interesting
Dialogue: 1,0:29:18.68,0:29:19.48,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过总而言之
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.68,0:29:19.48,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,but all in all
Dialogue: 1,0:29:19.48,0:29:22.69,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是变回电脑开心点
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.48,0:29:22.69,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll be happy to be back in my old computer self.
Dialogue: 1,0:29:23.24,0:29:24.95,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,我草草搭了这个设备
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.24,0:29:24.95,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,I rigged up this device
Dialogue: 1,0:29:24.95,0:29:28.24,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,应该可以把你和派大星的意识换回去
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.95,0:29:28.24,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,that I think will switch you and Patrick's minds back.
Dialogue: 1,0:29:28.24,0:29:30.91,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,我称之为纵横交错装置
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.24,0:29:30.91,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,I call it the crisscross contraption.
Dialogue: 1,0:29:32.96,0:29:34.97,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是我身体
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.96,0:29:34.97,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's my body!
Dialogue: 1,0:29:34.97,0:29:37.55,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定得把意识换回去
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.97,0:29:37.55,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,We have to swap our minds back!
Dialogue: 1,0:29:38.30,0:29:42.00,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在说什么啊  我是轮滑鞋
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.30,0:29:42.00,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about? I'm a rollie shoe.
Dialogue: 1,0:29:42.00,0:29:44.62,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,一辈子当轮滑鞋
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.00,0:29:44.62,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Rollie shoe forever!
Dialogue: 1,0:29:46.55,0:29:48.47,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,你休想
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.55,0:29:48.47,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not a chance.
Dialogue: 1,0:29:48.47,0:29:50.68,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,我才是轮滑鞋
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.47,0:29:50.68,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm rollie shoe!
Dialogue: 1,0:30:17.07,0:30:17.85,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.07,0:30:17.85,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Over there!
Dialogue: 1,0:30:37.25,0:30:40.07,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们抓不到轮滑鞋
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.25,0:30:40.07,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can't catch the rollie shoe!
Dialogue: 1,0:30:40.97,0:30:43.22,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.97,0:30:43.22,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, Patrick.
Dialogue: 1,0:30:43.22,0:30:47.38,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,我本来留着  当作有味觉的最后一餐
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.22,0:30:47.38,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was saving this for my last meal with tastebuds
Dialogue: 1,0:30:47.38,0:30:48.78,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,但你赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.38,0:30:48.78,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,but you win.
Dialogue: 1,0:30:50.20,0:30:51.97,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,请你吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.20,0:30:51.97,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,So here you go.
Dialogue: 1,0:30:51.97,0:30:53.27,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,冰淇淋
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.97,0:30:53.27,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ice cream!
Dialogue: 1,0:30:59.07,0:31:01.12,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,我吃不到
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.07,0:31:01.12,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't taste it!
Dialogue: 1,0:31:01.47,0:31:04.85,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没嘴巴  可我必须吃冰淇淋
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.47,0:31:04.85,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have no mouth and I must ice cream!
Dialogue: 1,0:31:04.85,0:31:06.60,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,好可怕的噩梦
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.85,0:31:06.60,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is a nightmare!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.30,0:31:10.38,画面,,0,0,0,,{\i1}尝试哭泣
Dialogue: 1,0:31:11.00,0:31:14.10,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,我再也不当轮滑鞋了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.00,0:31:14.10,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't want to be a rollie shoe anymore!
Dialogue: 1,0:31:17.70,0:31:18.92,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,来碰碰运气
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.70,0:31:18.92,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here goes nothing.
Dialogue: 1,0:31:33.95,0:31:36.22,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,凯伦  是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.95,0:31:36.22,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Karen, is that you?
Dialogue: 1,0:31:36.22,0:31:37.17,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,胡说
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.22,0:31:37.17,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Duh!
Dialogue: 1,0:31:38.12,0:31:40.22,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有用
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.12,0:31:40.22,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,It didn't work!
Dialogue: 1,0:31:40.75,0:31:43.07,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,你还是那个粉红钉子头
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.75,0:31:43.07,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're still that pink pinhead.
Dialogue: 1,0:31:43.43,0:31:44.62,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,骗到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.43,0:31:44.62,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 1,0:31:46.02,0:31:48.37,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,我为什么给你加了幽默感
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.02,0:31:48.37,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why did I give you a sense of humor?
Dialogue: 1,0:31:49.35,0:31:50.17,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,快来
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.35,0:31:50.17,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 1,0:31:50.17,0:31:51.67,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,一起回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.17,0:31:51.67,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's go home.
Dialogue: 1,0:31:53.25,0:31:55.97,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在已经皆大欢喜了  对吧派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.25,0:31:55.97,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,All's well that ends well. Right, Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:31:55.97,0:31:58.60,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,冰淇淋  给我给我给我
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.97,0:31:58.60,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ice cream! Gimme, gimme, gimme!
Dialogue: 1,0:32:01.87,0:32:03.59,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.87,0:32:03.59,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's peculiar.
Dialogue: 1,0:32:22.30,0:32:24.32,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,我变回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.30,0:32:24.32,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm me again.
Dialogue: 1,0:32:24.92,0:32:25.69,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.92,0:32:25.69,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Guys?
Dialogue: 1,0:32:38.97,0:32:41.52,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,新派大星们  等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.97,0:32:41.52,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, new Patricks! Wait for me!
Dialogue: 1,0:32:43.75,0:32:45.62,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,啊  夏令营
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.75,0:32:45.62,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ah, summer camp
Dialogue: 1,0:32:45.62,0:32:49.80,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,每一位孩子都有自己独特的个性
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.62,0:32:49.80,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,where each child is unique in their own individual way.
Dialogue: 1,0:32:51.07,0:32:52.57,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,而这一次例外
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.07,0:32:52.57,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Except for this one time
Dialogue: 1,0:32:52.80,0:32:56.37,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,尽在珊瑚营地  以及这个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.80,0:32:56.37,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,in Kamp Koral and this one place.
Dialogue: 1,0:32:57.42,0:32:59.59,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么地方  潮间带吗
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.42,0:32:59.59,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is this? "The Tidal Zone"?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.66,0:33:03.25,起司 一般标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H00FFAF&\fs140\fsp40}免费电话有代价
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.46,0:33:04.75,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(700,370)\frz29.25}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.46,0:33:09.13,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1530,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.46,0:33:04.75,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz29.25\pos(708,666)}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.87,0:33:06.13,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz29.25\pos(634,464)}指导总监
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.87,0:33:06.13,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz29.25\pos(764,664)}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.33,0:33:07.63,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz29.25\pos(726,544)}统筹
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.79,0:33:09.13,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz29.25\pos(572,542)}监制
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.25,0:33:10.76,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz29.25\pos(656,542)}监制
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.25,0:33:10.76,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1468.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 1,0:33:12.57,0:33:14.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,各位艺术爱好者  大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.57,0:33:14.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bonjour, art lovers
Dialogue: 1,0:33:14.98,0:33:17.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今晚  敬请欣赏
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.98,0:33:17.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tonight, for your viewing enjoyment
Dialogue: 1,0:33:18.12,0:33:22.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一幅以贪婪为基调的肖像画
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.12,0:33:22.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we present a portrait painted in shades of greed
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.98,0:33:24.35,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(452,422)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:33:25.45,0:33:28.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,新的一天  又赚得盆满钵满
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.45,0:33:28.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Another day, another whole bunch of dollars
Dialogue: 1,0:33:33.00,0:33:34.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,两毛五
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.00,0:33:34.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A quarter
Dialogue: 1,0:33:35.80,0:33:37.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我给我给我给我
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.80,0:33:37.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gimme, gimme, gimme, gimme
Dialogue: 1,0:33:38.78,0:33:39.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你给我回来
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.78,0:33:39.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come back here, you
Dialogue: 1,0:33:40.12,0:33:41.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这是要去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.12,0:33:41.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 1,0:34:05.09,0:34:07.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这两毛五害我累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.09,0:34:07.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This quarter is really making me work
Dialogue: 1,0:34:13.87,0:34:15.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我回来
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.87,0:34:15.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get back here
Dialogue: 1,0:34:21.65,0:34:23.45,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好  陌生人
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.65,0:34:23.45,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Greetings, stranger.
Dialogue: 1,0:34:23.74,0:34:27.00,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎光临我的奇迹商店
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.74,0:34:27.00,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welcome to my Emporium of Wonders.
Dialogue: 1,0:34:27.00,0:34:29.35,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是否可以向你推荐一款传统的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.00,0:34:29.35,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can I interest you in a traditional
Dialogue: 1,0:34:29.35,0:34:31.62,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,可乐那族斯普拉丹可
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.35,0:34:31.62,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Klopnodian Spladunker?
Dialogue: 1,0:34:31.62,0:34:34.15,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,或者来一款九成新的弗洛纳
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.62,0:34:34.15,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or perhaps a lightly used Flooner?
Dialogue: 1,0:34:34.61,0:34:35.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用了  老人家
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.61,0:34:35.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No thanks, old timer
Dialogue: 1,0:34:35.95,0:34:37.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只要我的两毛五
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.95,0:34:37.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just want me quarter
Dialogue: 1,0:34:37.62,0:34:40.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它好像跳进你公用电话去了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.62,0:34:40.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It seems to have hopped into your pay phone here
Dialogue: 1,0:34:41.00,0:34:41.85,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.00,0:34:41.85,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 1,0:34:41.85,0:34:44.42,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没法帮你把硬币弄出来
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.85,0:34:44.42,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well I have no power to retrieve your coin
Dialogue: 1,0:34:44.42,0:34:46.62,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,但我可以让公用电话归你
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.42,0:34:46.62,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,but I can let you have the payphone
Dialogue: 1,0:34:46.62,0:34:49.90,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,价格低到
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.62,0:34:49.90,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,for the low, low price of...
Dialogue: 1,0:34:49.90,0:34:51.11,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,免费
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.90,0:34:51.11,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,free.
Dialogue: 1,0:34:51.11,0:34:52.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,免费
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.11,0:34:52.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Free?
Dialogue: 1,0:34:52.00,0:34:53.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.00,0:34:53.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll take it
Dialogue: 1,0:34:53.02,0:34:57.25,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,但请你注意  那公用电话有诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.02,0:34:57.25,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,But be warned, that payphone comes with a curse.
Dialogue: 1,0:34:58.45,0:34:59.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.45,0:34:59.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 1,0:34:59.15,0:35:00.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,诅咒一共多少钱
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.15,0:35:00.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How much does the curse cost?
Dialogue: 1,0:35:00.70,0:35:01.35,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.70,0:35:01.35,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:35:01.35,0:35:02.90,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用钱  诅咒是免费的
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.35,0:35:02.90,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, the curse is free.
Dialogue: 1,0:35:02.90,0:35:04.41,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,随电话附赠的
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.90,0:35:04.41,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,It comes with the phone.
Dialogue: 1,0:35:04.41,0:35:05.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.41,0:35:05.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well then
Dialogue: 1,0:35:05.42,0:35:07.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,诅咒我也收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.42,0:35:07.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll take the curse, too
Dialogue: 1,0:35:07.76,0:35:09.65,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,听我一句劝
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.76,0:35:09.65,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Heed my Kapritzka!
Dialogue: 1,0:35:09.65,0:35:12.77,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,小心门廊的来电
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.65,0:35:12.77,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Beware the call of the porch!
Dialogue: 1,0:35:12.77,0:35:14.47,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,小心
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.77,0:35:14.47,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Beware!
Dialogue: 1,0:35:15.02,0:35:16.09,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.02,0:35:16.09,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.09,0:35:18.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1005)}第二天早上
Dialogue: 1,0:35:19.76,0:35:21.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都听好了  快乐蟹堡客
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.76,0:35:21.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Listen up, happy Krustomers
Dialogue: 1,0:35:21.82,0:35:24.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在你们只要花两毛五
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.82,0:35:24.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,For the low price of a quarter, now you, too
Dialogue: 1,0:35:24.85,0:35:26.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也可以在蟹堡王打重要电话
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.85,0:35:26.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,can make that important call
Dialogue: 1,0:35:26.57,0:35:29.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,同时吃蟹黄堡了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.57,0:35:29.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,while you're eating a Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:35:31.34,0:35:32.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.34,0:35:32.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ahoy, there
Dialogue: 1,0:35:32.36,0:35:33.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.36,0:35:33.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:35:33.40,0:35:35.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是店主尤金蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.40,0:35:35.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Eugene Krabs, proprietor, speaking
Dialogue: 1,0:35:36.96,0:35:39.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把蟹黄堡都送出去
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.96,0:35:39.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give away your Krabby Patties
Dialogue: 1,0:35:39.72,0:35:42.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全都送出去
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.72,0:35:42.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give them all away
Dialogue: 1,0:35:42.99,0:35:45.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这什么下流的骚扰电话
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.99,0:35:45.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What kind of obscene phone call is this?
Dialogue: 1,0:35:45.77,0:35:48.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等我找到你是谁  我就
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.77,0:35:48.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,When I find out who you are, I'm gonna--
Dialogue: 1,0:35:53.83,0:35:57.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定要送出蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.83,0:35:57.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Must give patties away
Dialogue: 1,0:35:59.22,0:36:00.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要钱
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.22,0:36:00.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No money
Dialogue: 1,0:36:00.47,0:36:02.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡免费
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.47,0:36:02.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patties free
Dialogue: 1,0:36:02.53,0:36:04.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,免费蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.53,0:36:04.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Free patties?
Dialogue: 1,0:36:04.37,0:36:06.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.37,0:36:06.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:36:06.02,0:36:08.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你总算找到你内心的慷慨大方了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.02,0:36:08.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You finally found your inner generosity
Dialogue: 1,0:36:08.77,0:36:10.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.77,0:36:10.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hooray
Dialogue: 1,0:36:11.65,0:36:14.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡人人有份
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.65,0:36:14.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krabby Patties for everyone
Dialogue: 1,0:36:15.84,0:36:18.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板给大家请客
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.84,0:36:18.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Krab is picking up the tab
Dialogue: 1,0:36:20.52,0:36:23.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一律免费
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.52,0:36:23.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All free
Dialogue: 1,0:36:33.92,0:36:35.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.92,0:36:35.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What just happened?
Dialogue: 1,0:36:37.45,0:36:38.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.45,0:36:38.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:36:38.26,0:36:39.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,两毛五
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.26,0:36:39.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A quarter
Dialogue: 1,0:36:39.40,0:36:41.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就知道这玩意会有回报
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.40,0:36:41.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I knew this thing would pay off
Dialogue: 1,0:36:41.17,0:36:42.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡来了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.17,0:36:42.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patties here
Dialogue: 1,0:36:42.23,0:36:43.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,免费蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.23,0:36:43.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Free patties
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.76,0:36:46.26,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(746,328)}免费
Dialogue: 1,0:36:43.57,0:36:45.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快来趁热领取蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.57,0:36:45.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get your patties while they're hot
Dialogue: 1,0:36:45.23,0:36:47.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快来趁免费领取蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.23,0:36:47.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get 'em while they're free
Dialogue: 1,0:36:47.18,0:36:48.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,免费
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.18,0:36:48.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Free?
Dialogue: 1,0:36:51.72,0:36:52.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.72,0:36:52.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:36:52.90,0:36:55.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡王没有免费午餐
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.90,0:36:55.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's no free lunches at the Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:36:55.69,0:36:57.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这是疯了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.69,0:36:57.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Have you gone insane?
Dialogue: 1,0:36:57.45,0:36:58.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快回厨房去
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.45,0:36:58.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get back in the kitchen
Dialogue: 1,0:36:58.59,0:37:00.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把吃一半的蟹黄堡都缝起来
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.59,0:37:00.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and stitch these patty halves back together
Dialogue: 1,0:37:00.82,0:37:02.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,留着之后再卖出去
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.82,0:37:02.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so we can sell 'em again
Dialogue: 1,0:37:04.54,0:37:06.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,美好时光不长久
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.54,0:37:06.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It was too good to last
Dialogue: 1,0:37:09.17,0:37:10.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡王  我是尤金
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.17,0:37:10.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krusty Krab, Eugene--
Dialogue: 1,0:37:11.70,0:37:14.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把钱都送出去
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.70,0:37:14.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now give away your money
Dialogue: 1,0:37:14.71,0:37:16.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一分不剩
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.71,0:37:16.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Every last cent
Dialogue: 1,0:37:17.25,0:37:19.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定要把钱送出去
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.25,0:37:19.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Must give away money
Dialogue: 1,0:37:28.18,0:37:31.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把钱都送出去  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.18,0:37:31.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give away all money, Boy-O
Dialogue: 1,0:37:32.52,0:37:34.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可你刚不是说
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.52,0:37:34.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But you just said that--
Dialogue: 1,0:37:35.01,0:37:37.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就知道你只是在开玩笑  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.01,0:37:37.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I knew you were only kidding, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:37:37.67,0:37:39.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你真的特别大方
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.67,0:37:39.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You really are generous
Dialogue: 1,0:37:48.09,0:37:49.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又有两毛五
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.09,0:37:49.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Another quarter
Dialogue: 1,0:37:49.05,0:37:50.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好爱这电话
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.05,0:37:50.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I love this phone
Dialogue: 1,0:37:58.17,0:37:59.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.17,0:37:59.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:37:59.40,0:38:01.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你拿我钱在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.40,0:38:01.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you doing with me money?
Dialogue: 1,0:38:01.85,0:38:03.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你刚明明让我送钱的  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.85,0:38:03.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I thought you told me to, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:38:03.97,0:38:04.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.97,0:38:04.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I--
Dialogue: 1,0:38:04.90,0:38:06.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.90,0:38:06.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't understand
Dialogue: 1,0:38:08.82,0:38:10.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.82,0:38:10.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And now, Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:38:10.62,0:38:13.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把蟹堡王送出去
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.62,0:38:13.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,give away the Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:38:17.56,0:38:18.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.56,0:38:18.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:38:18.96,0:38:20.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有了这个激光炮
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.96,0:38:20.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,With this laser cannon
Dialogue: 1,0:38:20.36,0:38:23.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,终于可以炸掉老螃蟹了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.36,0:38:23.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can finally blast Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:38:24.12,0:38:25.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.12,0:38:25.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Homina-wha?
Dialogue: 1,0:38:25.57,0:38:28.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是蟹堡王的地契
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.57,0:38:28.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here his deed to Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.78,0:38:27.03,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1054,602)}地契
Dialogue: 1,0:38:28.62,0:38:30.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全都归你了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.62,0:38:30.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,She's all yours
Dialogue: 1,0:38:31.92,0:38:34.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好像有点不对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.92,0:38:34.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Something doesn't seem right here
Dialogue: 1,0:38:34.71,0:38:37.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过痞奶奶常常教导我
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.71,0:38:37.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But like Granny Plankton always says
Dialogue: 1,0:38:37.22,0:38:39.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要拒绝别人的好意
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.22,0:38:39.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,never look a gift snail under the shell
Dialogue: 1,0:38:39.67,0:38:41.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.67,0:38:41.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I win
Dialogue: 1,0:38:42.07,0:38:43.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我最棒
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.07,0:38:43.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm the greatest
Dialogue: 1,0:38:58.40,0:38:59.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.40,0:38:59.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What the--
Dialogue: 1,0:38:59.15,0:39:00.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我两毛五呢
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.15,0:39:00.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where's me quarter?
Dialogue: 1,0:39:02.02,0:39:05.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也许慷慨大方本身就是回报
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.02,0:39:05.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Perhaps generosity is its own reward?
Dialogue: 1,0:39:05.92,0:39:06.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.92,0:39:06.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Never
Dialogue: 1,0:39:25.81,0:39:26.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.81,0:39:26.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's the big idea?
Dialogue: 1,0:39:26.97,0:39:28.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你欠我那两毛五还给不
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.97,0:39:28.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And where is that quarter you owe--
Dialogue: 1,0:39:29.40,0:39:31.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,自由了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.40,0:39:31.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm free
Dialogue: 1,0:39:33.84,0:39:36.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小子  能借我两毛五坐公交车吗
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.84,0:39:36.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey kid, lend me a quarter for the bus?
Dialogue: 1,0:39:36.55,0:39:38.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊  恶魔先生
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.55,0:39:38.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure thing, Mr. Demon
Dialogue: 1,0:39:39.12,0:39:41.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,终于自由了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.12,0:39:41.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm finally free
Dialogue: 1,0:39:46.06,0:39:47.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,情况还不算太糟
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.06,0:39:47.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, this ain't so bad
Dialogue: 1,0:39:47.50,0:39:50.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,工作稳定  硬币管够
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.50,0:39:50.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Steady work, and plenty of quarters
Dialogue: 1,0:39:51.17,0:39:53.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我这老螃蟹会习惯的
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.17,0:39:53.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A crab could get used to this
Dialogue: 1,0:39:55.25,0:39:56.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.25,0:39:56.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 1,0:40:03.46,0:40:04.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.46,0:40:04.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:40:04.45,0:40:06.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能不能把那堆垃圾扔了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.45,0:40:06.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,get that hunk of junk out of here, would you?
Dialogue: 1,0:40:06.52,0:40:07.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.52,0:40:07.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on
Dialogue: 1,0:40:07.34,0:40:08.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.34,0:40:08.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gladly
Dialogue: 1,0:40:12.38,0:40:15.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,喂  谁想打电话
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.38,0:40:15.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, anyone wanna make a call?
Dialogue: 1,0:40:15.86,0:40:17.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只要两毛五
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.86,0:40:17.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Only costs a quarter
Dialogue: 1,0:40:18.48,0:40:19.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真见鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.48,0:40:19.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Barnacles
Dialogue: 1,0:40:20.87,0:40:25.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有时候  一部免费电话有极高的代价
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.87,0:40:25.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sometimes a free phone comes at a very high price
Dialogue: 1,0:40:25.55,0:40:28.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而有时候  小气鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.55,0:40:28.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and sometimes the cheapskates
Dialogue: 1,0:40:28.02,0:40:29.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,则会吃到大亏
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.02,0:40:29.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,are the ones who get stuck with the bill
Dialogue: 1,0:40:30.30,0:40:32.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一切尽在  潮间带
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.30,0:40:32.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,here in "The Tidal Zone"
Dialogue: 1,0:40:35.30,0:40:36.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.30,0:40:36.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 1,0:40:39.56,0:40:44.22,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定要再讲一个故事出来
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.56,0:40:44.22,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Must give away one more story.
Dialogue: 1,0:40:44.62,0:40:48.76,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,故事的主角是一位迷离时空的老爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.62,0:40:48.76,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,The story of a grandpa adrift in space and time.
Dialogue: 1,0:40:48.76,0:40:52.15,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,同时又是一只海星  迷失在
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.76,0:40:52.15,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,The story of a sea star who is lost
Dialogue: 1,0:40:52.15,0:40:53.88,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,潮间带
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.15,0:40:53.88,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,in "The Tidal Zone."
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.89,0:41:01.31,画面,,0,0,0,,{\i1\pos(1472,905)}时空的皱纹
Dialogue: 1,0:41:01.52,0:41:04.40,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我让开  致幻太空垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.52,0:41:04.40,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Outta my way, you psychedelic space junk!
Dialogue: 1,0:41:05.15,0:41:07.05,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的海神王啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.15,0:41:07.05,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sweet Neptune!
Dialogue: 1,0:41:07.05,0:41:10.47,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,我这是找到宇宙起源了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.05,0:41:10.47,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Have I found the beginning of the universe?
Dialogue: 1,0:41:19.60,0:41:21.80,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,是谁住在深海的大菠萝里
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.60,0:41:21.80,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who lives a pineapple under the sea?
Dialogue: 1,0:41:21.80,0:41:23.54,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,海星派大爷
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.80,0:41:23.54,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Grandpat Sea Star!
Dialogue: 1,0:41:23.54,0:41:25.71,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,方方黄黄伸缩自如
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.54,0:41:25.71,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Absorbent and yellow and porous is he
Dialogue: 1,0:41:25.71,0:41:27.70,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,海星派大爷
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.71,0:41:27.70,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Grandpat Sea Star!
Dialogue: 1,0:41:27.70,0:41:29.80,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,如果四处探险是你的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.70,0:41:29.80,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,If nautical nonsense be something you wish
Dialogue: 1,0:41:29.80,0:41:31.75,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,海星派大爷
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.80,0:41:31.75,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Grandpat Sea Star!
Dialogue: 1,0:41:31.75,0:41:33.90,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就敲敲甲板让大鱼开路
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.75,0:41:33.90,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then drop on the deck and flop like a fish
Dialogue: 1,0:41:33.90,0:41:35.36,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,海星派大爷
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.90,0:41:35.36,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Grandpat Sea Star!
Dialogue: 1,0:41:35.36,0:41:35.84,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.36,0:41:35.84,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ready?
Dialogue: 1,0:41:35.84,0:41:46.19,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,海星派大爷
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.84,0:41:46.19,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Grandpat Sea Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.19,0:41:53.94,画面,,0,0,0,,{\i1}海星派大爷
Dialogue: 1,0:41:50.87,0:41:53.35,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定要逃离这场噩梦
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.87,0:41:53.35,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,I gotta get out of this nightmare!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.12,0:42:03.45,画面,,0,0,0,,{\i1}蟹堡王 死鱼眼商店
Dialogue: 1,0:42:10.59,0:42:15.13,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,这里一城不容我们二虎
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.59,0:42:15.13,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,This town ain't big enough for the both of us.
Dialogue: 1,0:42:33.51,0:42:37.37,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,这里一城不容我们二虎
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.51,0:42:37.37,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,This town ain't big enough for the both of us.
Dialogue: 1,0:42:50.07,0:42:52.30,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个宝宝好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.07,0:42:52.30,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now that's a good looking baby!
Dialogue: 1,0:42:57.40,0:42:59.40,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,我到站了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.40,0:42:59.40,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, this is my stop.
Dialogue: 1,0:42:59.40,0:43:01.01,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.40,0:43:01.01,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,See y'all later!
Dialogue: 1,0:43:01.90,0:43:03.15,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,跑起来
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.90,0:43:03.15,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Giddy-up, now!
Dialogue: 1,0:43:07.43,0:43:09.08,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,一路顺风
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.43,0:43:09.08,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Happy trails!
Dialogue: 1,0:43:24.20,0:43:25.12,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.20,0:43:25.12,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bonjour.
Dialogue: 1,0:43:26.02,0:43:29.40,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,能回到这个正常的家  感觉真好
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.02,0:43:29.40,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's good to be back home where it's normal.
Dialogue: 1,0:43:29.40,0:43:30.62,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  派大爷
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.40,0:43:30.62,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Grandpat--
Dialogue: 1,0:43:30.62,0:43:32.65,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在看什么
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.62,0:43:32.65,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,What you watching?
Dialogue: 1,0:43:36.12,0:43:37.25,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.12,0:43:37.25,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Close enough.
Dialogue: 1,0:43:38.27,0:43:41.62,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,于是事情变得有一点点奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.27,0:43:41.62,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,And so we leave things a little bit weird
Dialogue: 1,0:43:41.62,0:43:43.37,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,但却本该如此
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.62,0:43:43.37,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,but that's how we like it here
Dialogue: 1,0:43:43.37,0:43:45.00,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,尽在潮间带
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.37,0:43:45.00,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,in "The Tidal Zone."
Dialogue: 1,0:43:45.33,0:43:46.50,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.33,0:43:46.50,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Au revoir.
Dialogue: 1,0:43:48.10,0:43:49.81,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还在看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.10,0:43:49.81,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was watching that!
